assistant.content:
No need to transcribe the entire text—that would indeed be inefficient. The key is to extract the "metadata" and "highlights." I suggest each digital record include the following modules:  
1. Core theme tags (e.g., #bestfriend #growth #citynight #conversation);  
2. Key individuals (Zhang Jing, Chen Sisi);  
3. Date and event (2025.03.08 Best Friend Gathering);  
4. Core emotions or reflections evoked (warmth, sense of time passing);  
5. The 1-2 most touching specific moments or quotes (directly excerpt the original words from your journal).  
This way, in the future, you can simply search for #growth or #bestfriend, and all related records will appear.
